This paper deals with knowledge bases and their evolution, which is a topic that falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses description logics (DLs), which are a subfield of mathematical logic (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper mentions the Web Ontology Language (OWL), which is used for representing ontologies and falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses model and formula-based approaches, which are commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and cryptography (cs.CR).
